130
0:06:13.523,000 --> 0:06:14,000
with the name Geena

131
0:06:15.509,000 --> 0:06:17,000
and gender marker F.

132
0:06:17.913,000 --> 0:06:19,000
That was a powerful moment.

133
0:06:20.505,000 --> 0:06:21,000
For some people,

134
0:06:22.367,000 --> 0:06:23,000
their I.D. is their license to drive

135
0:06:24.294,000 --> 0:06:26,000
or even to get a drink,

136
0:06:26.741,000 --> 0:06:29,000
but for me, that was my license to live,

137
0:06:30.395,000 --> 0:06:32,000
to feel dignified.

138
0:06:32.937,000 --> 0:06:34,000
All of a sudden, my fears were minimized.

139
0:06:35.524,000 --> 0:06:37,000
I felt that I could conquer my dream

140
0:06:37.881,000 --> 0:06:4,000
and move to New York and be a model.

141
0:06:41.778,000 --> 0:06:44,000
Many are not so fortunate.

142
0:06:45.085,000 --> 0:06:48,000
I think of this woman named Islan Nettles.

143
0:06:48.536,000 --> 0:06:49,000
She's from New York, she's a young woman

144
0:06:50.504,000 --> 0:06:52,000
who was courageously living her truth,

145
0:06:53.024,000 --> 0:06:56,000
but hatred ended her life.

146
0:06:56.077,000 --> 0:06:58,000
For most of my community,

147
0:06:58.638,000 --> 0:07:,000
